question: What would be the impact on the 100m sprint world record if humans could run as fast as a peregrine falcon dives?

steps.content: What would be the impact on the 100m sprint world record if humans could run as fast as a peregrine falcon dives?

Searching for the diving speed of a peregrine falcon.
The peregrine falcon can dive at speeds up to 240 mph (386 km/h).
Calculating time to complete 100m at 240 mph: time = distance / speed = 100m / (240 mph in m/s).
